meta.title: Genomic epidemiology of Enteroviruses (EV) - 2C ORF
meta.description:
We gratefully acknowledge the authors, originating and submitting laboratories of the genetic sequences and metadata for sharing their work.


 
This visualization accompanies the article entitled: Phylogenetic analysis of enteroviruses from non-human primates reveals two new species within the genus Enterovirus.



The trees are rooted by default on human poliovirus type 1 (Mahoney strain, GenBank ID: V01148) for ease of visualization.
